<h2>Limiting the number of displayed results</h2>

<p>The following example limit the number of result to four items. The HTML5 specification recommends to limits between four to seven items.</p>

<p>Note: Using the same <code>datalist</code> for two different <code>input</code> may conflict when limiting the number of results.</p>

