<h2>Apply diferent type of filter</h2>

<p>The autocomplete implementation vary from browser. IE trend to show start of matching word, Chrome show any item that contains the string, Firefox also show any item that contains the string but limit the number of displayed result to five items.</p>

<p>Note: Using the same <code>datalist</code> for two different <code>input</code> may conflict when limiting the number of results.</p>

<p>Using the filter type work best when combined with <code>data-wb-limit</code> options</p> 

